levelDescription: This is a room with a white crib in it. It looks out of place.
This room is filled with babythings. The walls have painted unicorns and the shelves are filled with toys. Only thing missing is the crib...
A nursing room... and a changing table with a moldy pacifier on it. A funky smell surrounds this room..
A study. A nice comfy chair, books on the shelves and a decanter filled with a golden liquid and a used glass. Dust everywhere.
This room is a mess. Broken bottles and thrashed books. A nursery rhyme is pinned to the wall..
The doll almost looks like it is shivering in cold...
The doll looks unhappy. Is it... pucking it's lips?
Do you remember the nursery rhyme? It feels like you should recite it
A pink key on the floor. A door with a blueish tint slowly swings open on the east wall..
